OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHead disgusted by state of 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffood at his own school     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A head teacher has asked "how difficult
OL,6, is it to bake a potato?" in a          
OL,7, despairing letter to parents about the 
OL,8, state of food at his own school.       
OL,10,FJason Ashley, head of Redbridge        
OL,11,FCommunity School in Southampton, said  
OL,12,Fmeals served in its canteen were       
OL,13,F"completely unacceptable".             
OL,15,FHe blamed caterers Chartwells for the  
OL,16,Fissues and said he had no control over 
OL,17,Fwhat was on offer to pupils.           
OL,19,FThe firm has apologised and promised an
OL,20,F"immediate action plan".               
